In the INTEREST OF T.G., Minor Child, A.G., Father, Appellant, A.M., Mother, Appellant. No. 18-1195 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother and father appeal the termination of their respective parental rights in their child. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
